<subSubSection id="6DC56513FFEBFFE7E2C2A036CB3B7691" pageId="5" pageNumber="306" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="25603698FFEBFFE7E2C2A036CB3B7691" blockId="5.[151,1436,448,763]" pageId="5" pageNumber="306">
<emphasis id="17ABEA8AFFEBFFE7E2C2A036CF027600" bold="true" box="[199,322,592,618]" pageId="5" pageNumber="306">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
May be distinguished from other species of the genus by a combination of the following character states: sides (MA, MP) of 
<emphasis id="17ABEA8AFFEBFFE7E134A013CD0D76E4" box="[817,845,629,654]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="306">im</emphasis>
converging basally at low angle [
<taxonomicName id="E2DF4D1BFFEBFFE7E6DDA013CB3376E4" authorityName="Adams" authorityYear="1967" box="[1240,1395,629,655]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysopidae" genus="Archaeochrysa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neuroptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="306" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="paranervis">
<emphasis id="17ABEA8AFFEBFFE7E6DDA013CB3376E4" box="[1240,1395,629,655]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="306">A. paranervis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="E2DF4D1BFFEBFFE7E781A013CF4476D8" authority="Makarkin &amp; Antell &amp; Archibald, 2022" authorityName="Makarkin &amp; Antell &amp; Archibald" authorityYear="2022" class="Insecta" family="Chrysopidae" genus="Archaeochrysa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neuroptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="306" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cockerelli" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="17ABEA8AFFEBFFE7E781A013CBD576E5" box="[1412,1429,629,655]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="306">A</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="17ABEA8AFFEBFFE7E292A0FECF4476D8" box="[151,260,664,690]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="306">cockerelli</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="0C9857F1FFEBFFE7E30EA0FFCF2676D8" box="[267,358,665,691]" pageId="5" pageNumber="306" rank="species">
<emphasis id="17ABEA8AFFEBFFE7E30EA0FFCF1F76D9" bold="true" box="[267,351,665,691]" pageId="5" pageNumber="306">sp. nov</emphasis>
.
</taxonomicNameLabel>
: sides of 
<emphasis id="17ABEA8AFFEBFFE7E3D4A0FFCFAD76D8" box="[465,493,665,690]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="306">im</emphasis>
parallel and converging basally at steeper angle]; 2m-cu located distinctly proximad middle of 
<emphasis id="17ABEA8AFFEBFFE7E30BA0DBCF6A76BC" box="[270,298,701,726]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="306">im</emphasis>
[
<taxonomicName id="E2DF4D1BFFEBFFE7E339A0DBCF8676BD" authorityName="Makarkin &amp; Archibald" authorityYear="2013" box="[316,454,701,727]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysopidae" genus="Archaeochrysa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neuroptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="306" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="profracta">
<emphasis id="17ABEA8AFFEBFFE7E339A0DBCF8676BD" box="[316,454,701,727]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="306">A. profracta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="E2DF4D1BFFEBFFE7E3D3A0DBCC1376BC" authorityName="Archibald &amp; Makarkin" authorityYear="2015" box="[470,595,700,727]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysopidae" genus="Archaeochrysa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neuroptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="306" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="sanikwa">
<emphasis id="17ABEA8AFFEBFFE7E3D3A0DBCC1376BC" box="[470,595,700,727]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="306">A. sanikwa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
: slightly distad or slightly proximad middle of 
<emphasis id="17ABEA8AFFEBFFE7E671A0DBCAD076BC" box="[1140,1168,701,726]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="306">im</emphasis>
]; costal margin convex through costal space [
<taxonomicName id="E2DF4D1BFFEBFFE7E389A087CC547691" authorityName="Makarkin &amp; Archibald" authorityYear="2013" box="[396,532,737,763]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysopidae" genus="Archaeochrysa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neuroptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="306" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="profracta">
<emphasis id="17ABEA8AFFEBFFE7E389A087CC547691" box="[396,532,737,763]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="306">A. profracta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="E2DF4D1BFFEBFFE7E027A087CCDD7690" authorityName="Archibald &amp; Makarkin" authorityYear="2015" box="[546,669,736,763]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysopidae" genus="Archaeochrysa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neuroptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="306" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="sanikwa">
<emphasis id="17ABEA8AFFEBFFE7E027A087CCDD7690" box="[546,669,736,763]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="306">A. sanikwa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="E2DF4D1BFFEBFFE7E0AEA087CD037690" authorityName="Adams" authorityYear="1967" box="[683,835,737,763]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysopidae" genus="Archaeochrysa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neuroptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="306" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="paranervis">
<emphasis id="17ABEA8AFFEBFFE7E0AEA087CD037690" box="[683,835,737,763]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="306">A. paranervis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<emphasis id="17ABEA8AFFEBFFE7E154A087CD8A7690" box="[849,970,736,763]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="306">
<taxonomicName id="E2DF4D1BFFEBFFE7E154A087CD847690" baseAuthorityName="Carpenter" baseAuthorityYear="1935" box="[849,964,736,763]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysopidae" genus="Palaeochrysa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neuroptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="306" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="creedei">A. creedei</taxonomicName>
:
</emphasis>
not convex in middle of costal space].
</paragraph>
